spirit:fileSet.spirit:name: RTL
spirit:fileSet.spirit:description: This fileset describes the synthesizable RTL source files for this component

spirit:component.spirit:description: SIE-300 AXI5 Memory Protection Controller (MPC) acts as security gate for AXI transactions that target a memory interface. The security checks operate on block or page level, and are programmable by using the APB slave interface

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: ID_WIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: AXI ID width for all channels

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: QCLK_SYNC_EN
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Controls whether a 2-stage DFF synchronizer is inserted on the clock Q-Channel input

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: QPWR_SYNC_EN
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Controls whether a 2-stage DFF synchronizer is inserted on the power Q-Channel input

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: BLK_SIZE
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Memory Block size. The block size range is 256 bytes to 1MB. The default value of 7 gives a block size of 4KB
